features: Paint & Create Your Own Dinosaur Lamp Kit: This all-inclusive craft set allows you to design a one-of-a-kind dinosaur lamp. It includes a dinosaur lamp, 12 vibrant paint pots, 2 brushes, a palette, and 1 set of decoration stickers. Perfect for kids aged 6 and up, this kit offers a fun and enriching crafting experience, making it a great value for budding artists.

Unleash & Spark Creativity Painting Kit: This craft kit is the perfect gift for any child with a passion for creativity. It encourages kids to explore their imaginations, creating unique designs on their cat lamp. The DIY project not only offers hours of fun but also helps improve fine motor skills, stimulates creativity, and boosts self-confidence, making it an educational and enjoyable experience.

Safe and Fun Activities Art Supplies for All: The tools included in this craft kit are safe for children, giving you peace of mind as they create. Enjoy quality parent-child time with this arts and crafts set, ideal for both boys and girls aged 6 7 8 9 10 11 12. The included puff stickers add extra fun, allowing kids to personalize their cat lamp with eyes, eyelashes, scarves, and more.

Arts and Crafts for Kids Ages 6-12: This cat painting kit is ideal for children aged 6-12 and even adults. Select your favorite colors, dip your brush, and bring your cat lamp to life with your unique vision. It’s not just for kids—adults can also enjoy the creative process and reconnect with their inner child through this engaging art and craft activity.

Perfect Birthday Gift for Kids: This art kit makes a wonderful gift for boys and girls aged 6-12 who love to craft and draw. Whether it’s for Christmas, Halloween, birthdays, Easter, Valentine’s Day, or any other occasion, this set is sure to delight. It’s a fantastic arts and crafts project for kids to enjoy, resulting in a keepsake they can be proud of.
